      What are people saying about roofing services near Pittsburg, CA?

      This is a review for a roofing business near Pittsburg, CA:

      "I have some advice for anyone considering using East Bay Roofing to renew their roof. They are definitely the right choice. My sister's roof was pretty torn up and had wood rot all around the nearly the entire edge of the roof including about half of the rafters. These guys have an impressive work ethic. They had two layers of old shingles off, all the roof rot repaired, all of the rafters replaced, new gutters and downspouts installed, and had the roof re-shingled entirely in just a couple of days. It was amazing to watch them work so skillfully and efficiently. They even kept the entire property clean. Tony is the Joe Montana of roofing. The final result is nothing less than breathtaking."
